http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Vijayawada/Session-on-leadership-skills-time-management/article14017306.ece

The Indian Society for Technical Education (ISTE) chapter of PVP Siddhartha Institute of Technology on Saturday organised seminars on ‘Personality Development’ for third year engineering students and on ‘Time Management’ for faculty members.Senior manager of Hyderabad-based First America Dwaraka Ramana and Sailaja Manukonda doled out tips to students on improving communication skills, leadership skills and body language. They said these factors would play an important role during campus placement drive.In the afternoon session, faculty members of the college were given tips on time management. Principal K. Sivaji Babu said such programmes could be of immense help both to students and faculty members.